content: Lastly, I'm pleased to reiterate our 2022 full year financial guidance, including CpG 1018 adjuvant revenues, expected to be between $550 million and $600 million, with approximately 60% gross margin for the year, reflecting the economics associated with the remaining firm under our commercial supply agreements, R&D expenses in the range of $50 million to $60 million, SG&A expenses in the range of $130 million to $140 million and interest expense of approximately $7 million.
